      <span style="font-size:14px;">附有关个人简历表（每人一表）和身份证、学历证书、职称资质证书等证明文件（复印件加盖公章）<br /> &nbsp;<br /> 供应商名称（公章）：<br /> 法定代表人或授权代表（签字）：<br /> 年&nbsp; 月&nbsp; 日<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</span>
